                     throws IridaWorkflowNotFoundException,

        Start a new pipeline
        Parameters:
        id - - pipeline identifier
        request - - details about the request to start the pipeline
        locale - - currently logged in users locale
        Returns:
        The id of the new AnalysisSubmission, if more than one are kicked off, then the first id is returned.
        Throws:
        IridaWorkflowNotFoundException - thrown if the workflow cannot be found
        ReferenceFileRequiredException - thrown if a reference file is required and not sent (should not happen).
